Chatbot with Purple Theme
A chatbot application built with Dash and Dash Bootstrap Components, featuring interactive capabilities like graph generation, CSV processing, and generative AI responses. This project is designed to be visually appealing and functional, leveraging advanced AI models for dynamic responses.

Features
Chat Interface: A user-friendly interface for interacting with the bot.
CSV File Upload: Upload CSV files for data processing and visualization.
Dynamic Graph Generation: Supports various types of graphs (bar, line, scatter, etc.) using Plotly.
Generative AI Integration: Enhanced responses powered by Google Generative AI.
PDF Conversion: Converts CSV data to PDF for easy sharing and analysis.
Prerequisites
Before running the application, ensure you have the following installed:

Python 3.7 or higher
Required Python libraries (see Installation below)
Installation
Clone the Repository:

bash
Copy code
git clone https://github.com/your-repo/chatbot-purple-theme.git
cd chatbot-purple-theme
Set Up Virtual Environment:

bash
Copy code
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate   # For Linux/Mac
venv\Scripts\activate      # For Windows
Install Dependencies:

bash
Copy code
pip install -r requirements.txt
Set Environment Variables: Create a .env file in the project root and include your Google Generative AI API key:

makefile
Copy code
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
Running the Application
Start the Server:

bash
Copy code
python app.py
Access the Application: Open your web browser and navigate to http://127.0.0.1:8050.

Usage
Chat with the Bot:

Type a message in the input box and click Send.
Upload a CSV File:

Click the ðŸ“‚ button to upload a CSV file.
The bot will process the file and provide a graph or analysis based on the content.
Generate Graphs:

The bot supports various graph types, including bar, line, scatter, and pie charts.
Convert CSV to PDF:

Ask the bot to generate a PDF from the uploaded CSV file.
